EmailTemplate.description: Cover email for MPN Serilization Spreadsheet to be attached and sent thru Case
EmailTemplate.name: External MPN Serilaization Request Cover email
EmailTemplate.subject: MPN Serialization Information Request
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName},
Attached is our new serialization spreadsheet template (designed for automatic electronic processing). Both Stafford and PLUS can be entered on the same sheet by indicating GS in the Record identifier column for Stafford borrowers and PL for PLUS borrowers. All columns should be kept in the exact order as in the template.
I am also attaching the layout specs which give the acceptable format for each field.
Please let me know if you have any questions.
Thank you, {!User.Name} {!User.Title}
The content of this email is confidential and proprietary to American Student Assistance. It is intended only for the above-named individual or entity and for the purpose indicated and may not be reproduced or distributed without permission of the sender. Please notify the sender or ASA if you received this email in error.
